>> servings: 4

Wash @Rice and keep it aside.

Cut @Onion{2 pcs}, @Garlic{4 pcs} and @Ginger and start sauteing them in @Oil until their colour changes.

Add @Chilli powder{}, @Garam masala{}, @Turmeric, @Jeera powder{} and @Coriander in it. Mix well.

Mix rice with this masala and keep for ~{4 mins}.

Add @Salt to this mixture and add cold water until it submerges all the stuff in your pot.

Keep in mid flame and leave for 10-15 mins.

